        <h2 class="mb-4">A Corner for Taipei: Our Story</h2>
        <p>As someone who live and work in Taipei City, I've always been captivated by the vibrant pulse of this city—from the outdoor live show and the indie markets, to starlit runs along the riverside and festivals for families.</p>
        <p>But I often felt a small sense of regret. Information about these wonderful events felt scattered across countless different websites, social media pages, and bulletin boards. Too often, I’d find out about something amazing only after it had already ended, realizing I had missed out on a great experience happening just around the corner.</p>
        <p>And so, Taipei Fun Finder was born.</p>
        <p>It started with a simple idea: to create a clean, user-friendly, and dedicated platform that brings all of Taipei’s outdoor activities, big and small, into one place. Whether you're a lifelong resident, a newcomer to the city, or a traveler just passing through, we hope this site helps you easily discover every surprising and delightful side of Taipei.</p>
        <p>More than just a tool, we envision this site as a community bulletin board. Many of the best events come from independent creators, neighborhood communities, and passionate local shops. They deserve to be seen.</p>
        <h4 class="mt-4">You're Invited to Be a Part of It</h4>
        <p>If you or a friend are hosting an event—be it a concert, a pet gathering, a sports competition, or even a small neighborhood party—we would be thrilled to <strong>feature it for free</strong> and share your passion with more people.</p>
